Notes: How to release a new version
-----------------------------------

via https://cookiecutter-pypackage.readthedocs.io/en/latest/pypi_release_checklist.html

.. code-block:: console

    # Run the tests
    py.test
    make lint

    # Update history
    vi HISTORY.rst
    git add HISTORY.rst
    git commit -m "Changelog for upcoming release 0.1.1."

    # Update version
    bumpversion minor

    # Push
    git push && git push --tags


